","tid":2423404,"uid":264362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"274e97b753c3d7fec606b02069a302f0668a79e6","tid":2423404,"uid":13173,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b801452c80fee90c38bd5507bfcd5b7546245c1e","tid":2423404,"uid":367224,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ae1fa749382446948473aadab630aa6955a74d2b","tid":2423404,"uid":13173,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:20:11.000Z","msg":"唔同。<br />\n符號同reasoning一定要用英文/印歐語言<br />\n(from &ldquo;x, y, z&rdquo; to &ldquo;if and only if&rdquo;)<br />\n<br />\n否則令人容易思維混亂，尤其係漢語呢類冇咁講究邏輯嘅語言"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T09:29:08.000Z","msg":"當且僅當/若且唯若聽過未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"硬譯。<br />\n不知你現實會咁講嘢否?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:22:00.000Z","msg":"if and only if英文人現實又會咁講？"},{"pid":"87c068bae4adc04df422d37620f0b21dee460c33","tid":2423404,"uid":245552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"會。<br />\n中文每個阿拉伯數目字都只係音節，理解起嚟比較快，容易建立紮實基礎，如九因歌就係成功嘅例子。<br />\n英文相對中文煩少少，每個數字音節唔同，基礎比較花時間建立，但去到較高階嘅理論係英文佔優，因為好多理論術語都係西方建立，呢啲術語翻譯咗做中文反而冇咁傳神。<br />\n某啲語言例如法文嘅數字邏輯直頭係語言影響數理嘅代表例子，如中英文嘅70，佢哋會讀成60+10；80讀成4*20。"},{"pid":"7eac67230b117a3b3d1d5c3056042e7173a1483c","tid":2423404,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ef171efb27c6ade2d5496df1d5a2531fb9c17aa","tid":2423404,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:26:01.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用德文學個腦唔係好轉到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:40:35.000Z","msg":"same<br />\n用德文上measure theory嗰陣喺到心諗佢講緊乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(不過唔知會唔會用英文都一樣)"},{"pid":"b674f28cbd25e745a5911ba6aef1a8f8124c7515","tid":2423404,"uid":369321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T18:17:50.000Z","msg":"拉丁文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nQED"},{"pid":"1fa91e6ef8be2ca6a8d890a4e268c215f34542b6","tid":2423404,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5c28fe9ba4154189830b289912051efb4c783bd","tid":2423404,"uid":328681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae1fa749382446948473aadab630aa6955a74d2b","tid":2423404,"uid":13173,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1c013fad7440f5be11dcc9c72692fa3ec4d4a68a","tid":2423404,"uid":272677,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T17:55:33.000Z","msg":"數一向用數專用符號溝通，用日文定俄文都一樣"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:20:11.000Z","msg":"唔同。<br />\n符號同reasoning一定要用英文/印歐語言<br />\n(from &ldquo;x, y, z&rdquo; to &ldquo;if and only if&rdquo;)<br />\n<br />\n否則令人容易思維混亂，尤其係漢語呢類冇咁講究邏輯嘅語言"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:45:53.000Z","msg":"但如果用非母語學，前提係要熟習咗英文嘅意思，先可以理解邏輯上嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似中學咁，其實唔會話比你知variable字面上點解就直接教點operate?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反而仲混亂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:55:01.000Z","msg":"我就係失敗嘅例子😞人大左英文好左即刻冇事"},{"pid":"5221a12960e0d9f567db2a9920d17285d8874c13","tid":2423404,"uid":365711,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:24:37.000Z","msg":"以前睇過一篇paper關於語言同數學，好多年前睇，唔記得title係乜。<br />\n<br />\n裡面指出，有啲部落語言去到乜啲數字就冇一個specific嘅terms，所以佢哋係冇辦法處理數字，因此學唔識數學<br />\n<br />\n因此，語言對數學嘅理解有一定程度嘅影響。但係中文同英文都係世界語言，應該唔會構成好大嘅差距。<br />\n<br />\nintuitively，我覺得對於學生而言，比較大嘅分野在於佢哋對該語言嘅邏輯性字眼有冇不同程度嘅理解。例如，對於佢哋嚟講，if and only if定係當且僅當更容易理解？"},{"pid":"09c490e26d2e468e6f90cd055053b53d55c0afd0","tid":2423404,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:39:07.000Z","msg":"非歐幾何嗰啲？"},{"pid":"94912642dfa2cb401c8586b2ebe09d048e1c8605","tid":2423404,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a3bb0b7f2d10eaf6b8dac79ccf4929548d5777f","tid":2423404,"uid":3441,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ae1fa749382446948473aad